Persona - College Student
William is a 22 year old college junior located in Whitewater Wisconsin. 
He spends his days working on his classes for architecture, and his nights working on 
projects for a long term unpaid internship with a local construction company. 
He was born in Vernon Hills Illinois to jewish parents, where his father was an electrician and 
his mother was an account executive. His younger sibling is diabetic, 
and helping care for them shaped how he views technology in his daily life. 

As a member of Gen Z, he knows enough of technology to get around basic safeguards,
but turns away from any inconvenience or extra hoops he might have to jump through. 
He is actively discussing his finances with his fiancee, and they are looking for a city they 
can both move to once they graduate. He is hoping his current finances can last him until then, 
and wants a better way to grasp his expenditure of money.
